<plot>During the Massacre at Wounded Knee, an Army Lieutenant murdered Chief War Eagle and stole his Sacred PeacePipe, trapping the eagle spirit inside. Over a hundred years later, the Lieutenant's great-granddaughter finds the pipe and other stolen Native American artifacts buried in a box and decides to show them at a gallery for people to see. She soon finds out that one man with long black hair wants to do more than "see" the pipe and that he will stop at nothing to retrieve it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?649258</url></doc>
